              <section>

                  
          <div data-content-element-selector="p, .js-buylink-item-container" data-allowed-classes-selector="js-buylink-item-container">
                <p>The Xbox game <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/games/indiana-jones-and-the-great-circle/" data-ref-id="5000-525173">Indiana Jones and the Great Circle</a> came to PS5 on April 17 and it had a strong debut, it seems. Tracking firm <a href="https://bsky.app/profile/matpiscatella.bsky.social/post/3lnv5qiaxak2q" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Circana reports</a> that the game was the best-selling title in the US during its launch week. However, it did not come close to being one of the most-played games on PS5.</p><p>The Great Circle's debut on PS5 was the first time the game reached No. 1 on the sales charts for a given week. The Xbox and PC versions debuted in December 2024 and did not make it to No. 1 in the US during their launch weeks. Players on both platforms had access to the game via Game Pass Ultimate.</p>



    
