            <title><![CDATA[Game Release Overshadowed By Oblivion Remastered Is Jokingly Being "Re-released"]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/game-release-overshadowed-by-oblivion-remastered-is-jokingly-being-re-released/1100-6531174/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f</link>
